first install the typescript
npm install -g typescript = tsc --version 
  it  stand for typsctipt compiler

npm install -g ts-node   

package.json contain project configuration
-------------->  to create npm init -y

tsconfig.json it is typescript config file which take care of which version of js it it converting
-------------->  to create tsc --init 


it gives us type defination for node js
--------------> npm install @types/node

it gives us type defination for express
--------------> npm install @types/express

to get dist folder --------> npx tsc


devDependencies are those packages in the package.json file that you need only for project development purposes

npm i -D nodemon for nodemon for development purpose











// run npm run build first

